titles.title: For the relief of Diana Gecaj Engstrom.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on the Judiciary.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Immigration, Border Security, and Claims.

bill.summary: 6/14/2005--Introduced. Declares Diana Gecaj Engstrom to be eligible for issuance of an immigrant visa or for adjustment of status to that of an alien lawfully admitted for permanent residence under the Immigration and Nationality Act.
